As 12-year-old Rachael is a witness to the psychopath Patrick Batemans murder of her baby girl. Rachael takes a cold revenge on Bateman and performs his life to eradicate the serial killer. Later in life she is seeking employment as assistant to Professor Starkman - the man who knows more about serial killers throughout the country. But it is not so easy for Rachael to get the job. Other candidates, including a psychiatrist, standing in the way. What would a serial killer to do in that situation? Eliminate the problems, of course!
